= Code Example

Here's how easy it is to create
formatted content:

```typst
#let highlight(content) = {
  rect(
    fill: yellow.lighten(80%),
    inset: 8pt,
    radius: 4pt,
    content
  )
}

#highlight[This text is highlighted!]
```

